track_notes: 1.4 mile hike with with 760 EG along the Appalachian Trail. Plenty of parking is available at Tellico Gap (35.268, -83.572) where the AT crosses Otter Creek/Tellico Road. There is a shorter (0.9 miles) route following the old footbed of the AT along a gated FS road from Tellico Gap, but it is obviously a steeper climb than on the AT. There is a large fire tower converted to an observation deck that provides outstanding views.
